<section id="section3" class="panel">
    <h1 class="user-panel-heading">
        Welcome to my movie world!
    </h1>

    <p>
     Movies play a significant role in our lives. We all have memories of that one movie which makes us feel home, one which is with you in your thick and thin. Movies which has been a part of our life while growing up and have now become our best friend. Here are my favorites and the list goes on.
    </p>

    <h4>Click on the movie name to know more.</h4>

    <div class="team">
        <!-- loop through all our team members and put their info on the page -->
        {{#each movie}} {{!-- this is like a JS forEach loop --}}
        <div class="user-panel">
            <img class="m-image" src="images/{{image}}" alt="movie image">
            <a href="{{ID}}" class="u-link">
                See More Info
            </a>
            <h1>{{Name}}</h1>
        </div>
        {{/each}}
    </div>

    <!-- this will be filled in on the client side when we render our AJAX data -->
    <section class="lightbox">
        <span class="close">x</span>
        <div class="sidebar">
            <img src="" alt="larger bio image">
        </div>

        <div class="lb-content">
            {{!-- render the database content here --}}
        
        </div>
    </section>
</section>
